Unsourced material may be challenged and removed. *Find sources:* "Alexandra North" – news **·** newspapers **·** books **·** scholar **·** JSTOR *(July 2018)* *(Learn how and when to remove this message)*Subzone of Bukit Merah Planning Area in Central Region, Singapore **Alexandra North** ([Chinese](/wiki/Chinese_language): 亚历山大北) is a subzone within the planning area of [Bukit Merah](/wiki/Bukit_Merah), [Singapore](/wiki/Singapore), as defined by the [Urban Redevelopment Authority](/wiki/Urban_Redevelopment_Authority) (URA). Its boundary is made up of the Alexandra Canal and Prince Charles Square in the north; Tanglin Road in the west; Alexandra Road in the south; and Delta Road in the east.
